---
import SectionTitle from "../SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section class="product-faq">

    <div class="container">

        <SectionTitle
            tag="FAQ"
            title="Frequently Asked Questions"
        />

        <div class="faq-list">

            <details class="faq-item">

                <summary>What grades of cashew kernels do you supply?</summary>

                <p>
                    We supply premium Cambodian cashew kernels including
                    WW180, WW210, WW240, WW320, WW450, LP and SP grades.
                </p>

            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">

                <summary>Do you offer OEM or private label services?</summary>

                <p>
                    Yes. We provide OEM and private label packaging
                    tailored to your brand and market requirements.
                </p>

            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">

                <summary>What is your minimum order quantity (MOQ)?</summary>

                <p>
                    MOQ depends on the product type and packaging.
                    Please contact our sales team for detailed quotations.
                </p>

            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">

                <summary>Which countries do you export to?</summary>

                <p>
                    We serve both domestic and international markets
                    and welcome partnerships worldwide.
                </p>

            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">

                <summary>How can I request a quotation?</summary>

                <p>
                    Simply visit our Contact page or click the
                    "Request Quote" button to get in touch with us.
                </p>

            </details>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>